atic uncertainty on the diphoton mass resolution. No\nsignificant deviations from the predictions of the Standard Model are found.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 29 Aug 2014 17:35:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 9 Sep 2014 08:47:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-12-31"}
