unt of information that can be\ntransmitted by light through silicon is the key element in future information\nsystems. Results presented here are not only applicable to silicon but also to\nother semiconductor optical channels.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 30 Aug 2014 09:24:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-09-02"}
